sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Your app
    participant Auth as Auth Server
    participant API as Perfect Flight API
    App->>Auth: POST /oauth2/token (client_id + client_secret)
    Auth-->>App: 200 { access_token, expires_in, token_type }
    App->>API: GET /v1/... · Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
    API-->>App: 200 + requested resource
